# Pixel Art Submission

## Cyberpunk Cityscape

A 64x64 pixel art depiction of a futuristic cyberpunk cityscape at night, featuring neon-lit skyscrapers, holographic billboards, and a glowing moon reflected in rain-slicked streets. Created to evoke the intersection of technology and urban creativity that defines the FreelanceFlow platform — where independent builders craft their own futures in a digital landscape.

Canvas size: 64x64 pixels. Format: PNG with transparency.